# Web UI & Brand

Full guide: `web/docs/brand-guide.md`

## Structure

- **Hub** (`app/page.tsx`, `components/hub/`): program picker only — no product nav
- **Products** (`app/{product}/layout.tsx`): isolated nav per product; one **All Programs** link to `/`
- Products: `shooting-challenge`, `dribbling-challenge`, `kids-ref-now`

## Visual rules

- Use tokens from `app/globals.css` — official kit: blue `#0034B7`, orange `#FF8B00`
- **Base UI:** near-black `#0A0A0A`, white headlines, gray body — blue/orange as **accents only**, not full-page color washes
- Full guide: `web/docs/brand-guide.md` (127_SI_Brand_Kit)
- Logo: `BRAND_LOGOS` in `lib/brand.ts` — horizontal V1 on hub hero + product headers; circle for nav/footer/favicon
- **Maven Pro** for UI type; Magistral when web license available
- **No emoji** as icons on hub or product chrome
- **No cartoon** mascots, clip art, or playful illustration style
- **No per-product rainbow accents** (sky/violet/etc.) on hub cards — monochrome cards + brand orange/blue highlights
- Stats/XP/ranks: `font-mono`
- Small labels only: uppercase + letter-spacing

## Tailwind

- Prefer existing tokens; extend `globals.css` for new semantic colors
- Panels: `bg-card border border-white/[0.08]` on dark base
- CTAs: solid `bg-brand-orange` or white-outline secondary — avoid orange gradients everywhere

## Incremental delivery

- Ship hub + one product at a time; **Coming Soon** placeholders for unfinished apps
- Do not mix nav items across products
